1
00:00:07,407 --> 00:00:08,807
It's not like we're on a reality show.

2
00:00:08,808 --> 00:00:10,128
What's with the surprise mission?

3
00:00:11,111 --> 00:00:12,345
Oh, we have a task.

4
00:00:14,214 --> 00:00:15,582
Cooking dinner.

5
00:00:16,716 --> 00:00:18,350
We need to prep the ingredients.

6
00:00:18,351 --> 00:00:19,351
I'll do it.

7
00:00:22,322 --> 00:00:24,356
I can't let a sick person do the work.

8
00:00:24,357 --> 00:00:25,959
Here, just sit down.

9
00:00:30,730 --> 00:00:32,031
Take a break and rest.

10
00:00:32,032 --> 00:00:33,867
We don't want you getting any worse.

11
00:00:34,134 --> 00:00:35,135
I've got this.

12
00:00:35,735 --> 00:00:36,636
Is this part of your persona?

13
00:00:36,637 --> 00:00:39,597
Look how thoughtful I am. [TN: The
"I" here is forced cute self-appelation]

14
00:00:44,978 --> 00:00:47,056
You're supposed to chop
the cabbage before washing it.

15
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:48,348
I know that.

16
00:00:48,882 --> 00:00:50,884
I'm just giving it a quick rinse first.

17
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:54,420
Let me do it.

18
00:00:56,456 --> 00:00:57,456
Sit down.

19
00:01:03,930 --> 00:01:05,165
Watch out.

20
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:11,871
How are you planning to cook the cabbage?

21
00:01:12,105 --> 00:01:13,907
Isn't this how you shred it for tonkatsu?

22
00:01:15,608 --> 00:01:16,810
You want tonkatsu?

23
00:01:20,447 --> 00:01:22,048
Stop distracting me.

24
00:01:30,323 --> 00:01:32,224
It'll be midnight by the time you're done.

25
00:01:32,225 --> 00:01:33,258
Besides, when have you ever...

26
00:01:33,259 --> 00:01:35,099
chopped something
without cutting yourself?

27
00:01:36,396 --> 00:01:37,897
Fine, tell you what.

28
00:01:38,231 --> 00:01:39,531
I'll handle the prep work,

29
00:01:39,532 --> 00:01:40,892
and you can do the actual cooking.

30
00:01:41,801 --> 00:01:42,801
Deal.

31
00:01:47,874 --> 00:01:49,642
I guess everyone has their strengths.

32
00:01:49,976 --> 00:01:51,536
Your technique is actually pretty good.

33
00:01:51,978 --> 00:01:52,946
Didn't you know?

34
00:01:52,947 --> 00:01:54,247
I'm actually a certified chef.

35
00:02:02,088 --> 00:02:03,888
You really don't pay
attention to me, do you?

36
00:02:04,357 --> 00:02:05,724
I'm not like you.

37
00:02:05,725 --> 00:02:07,660
The company does all the research for you.

38
00:02:10,096 --> 00:02:11,463
I looked that up myself.

39
00:02:11,464 --> 00:02:13,099
It had nothing to do with the company.

40
00:02:18,638 --> 00:02:19,506
What are you, a rabbit?

41
00:02:19,507 --> 00:02:20,907
You really like eating raw veggies.

42
00:02:25,512 --> 00:02:26,512
Careful.

43
00:02:33,353 --> 00:02:34,420
You're still burning up.

44
00:02:34,787 --> 00:02:35,854
Go get some rest.

45
00:02:35,855 --> 00:02:36,990
I can handle the rest.

46
00:02:37,557 --> 00:02:38,597
Let's just do it together.

47
00:02:39,092 --> 00:02:39,993
That 'cold and aloof' persona of yours...

48
00:02:39,994 --> 00:02:41,161
is a total lie, isn't it?

49
00:02:41,694 --> 00:02:42,928
Who said I wanted to work with you?

50
00:02:42,929 --> 00:02:43,929
Just go.

51
00:02:44,397 --> 00:02:45,464
I'm going to take a shower then.

52
00:02:45,465 --> 00:02:46,465
A shower?

53
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,780
Just don't go passing out in the bathroom.

54
00:02:49,536 --> 00:02:50,856
I can't sleep if I don't wash up.
